SSHD = the daemon (receiver) â†’ runs on the remote machine (like your EC2). It sits there listening on port 22, waiting for SSH clients to connect.
So the flow looks like this:
Your terminal (ssh)  ---->  Internet  ---->  EC2 server (sshd on port 22)
